metadata.name: Never Enough
metadata.description: Why does anyone make anything? The reason is because there is a want or a need, this is the basis for all creation. What happens when both a want and a need is present, the want to create and the need for it to be done as it was visualized. From this mixture a dangerous drive to attain perfection is born. When your ambitions line up like that, everything you make will truly be never enough.
